        </item>
        <item>
            <title>網民：95% 人分不出 30 與 60fps  認為遊戲有 30fps 便已足夠</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/12/30-fps/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=30-fps</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/12/30-fps/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 14:00:27 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[任天堂]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[異界鎖鏈]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1223822</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">傳聞中任天堂會推出新機，惟一直只聞樓梯響，有玩家期望新一代主機擁有更高 fps，但有玩家則唱反調指大部份人不會發覺 30fps 與 60fps 畫面的分別，因此認為 30fps 已足夠。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">FYI the game is Nintendo New IP Astral Chain. Develop by The GODS Platinum Games. </p><p>Highly rated and regarded as one of the BEST Action games of All-Time</p><p>Innovative intense combat that is fluid, addictive, and amazing <a href="https://t.co/7xHn4lR4FZ">pic.twitter.com/7xHn4lR4FZ</a></p><p>&mdash; NintenGOD (@AesirMalos) <a href="https://twitter.com/AesirMalos/status/1765771810455294129?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">March 7, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p style="text-align: center;">▲X 用家 AesirMalos 引用《異界鎖鏈》的遊戲畫面，指該遊戲「戰鬥流暢、令人上癮、玩法也很創新。」</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">X 用家 AesirMalos 引用了白金工作室《異界鎖鏈》的遊戲畫面，指該遊戲「戰鬥流暢、令人上癮、玩法也很創新。」亦稱其為「史上最佳動作遊戲」，其他不重視 30fps 畫面的玩家會忽略這款傑作，而自己就不會。AesirMalos 再回覆指 95% 的人無法區分 30fps 和 60fps 之間的區別。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">This game is Astral Chain. One of the smoothest playing games I&#39;ve ever played.</p><p>No one knew it was 30fps until after Digital foundry said it was a cople days after release</p><p>&mdash; NintenGOD (@AesirMalos) <a href="https://twitter.com/AesirMalos/status/1765414047682285829?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">March 6, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p style="font-weight: 400;">AesirMalos 再有新留言指當年推出《異界鎖鏈》時，未有人知道其為 30fps 製作，直到遊戲推出後才知道。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://twitter.com/AesirMalos/status/1765771810455294129?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1765771810455294129%7Ctwgr%5E77074626222052c764cfb611da3abee3ad5233e3%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fgame.ettoday.net%2Farticle%2F2698274.htm">X</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/13/nintendo-switch-2-will-reportedly-have-backwards-compatibility/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">任天堂 Switch 2 最新傳聞，向後兼容能力提升舊遊戲畫質</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/12/30-fps/game-channel/">網民：95% 人分不出 30 與 60fps  認為遊戲有 30fps 便已足夠</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
